### Current Behavior

`nx serve host` is not starting up the remote server. It says:  Starting module federation dev-server for host with 0 remotes.

even `--dev-remotes` seems to have the same issue

### Expected Behavior

Should serve the remote apps

### GitHub Repo

_No response_

### Steps to Reproduce

Create an angular host and remotes.. note the remote apps are not being served

